com.ibm.team.repository.common.query.ast

Interface IField

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IFilterElement, ISelectionElement
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IBooleanField, IDateTimeField, IEnumField, INumericField, IStringField, IUUIDField

    public interface IField
extends IFilterElement, ISelectionElement
    Represents a field that can be queried on. A field can be a IStringField or a INumericField or a IBooleanField or a IUUIDField or a IEnumField.
    Since:
    0.5

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      IPredicate _isNull()
      Returns a predicate that evaluates to true if the value of the query field is null
      boolean isRedactable()
      Returns true if the server side query service should redact the value of this field from the results if the query's redaction conditions are met.
      com.ibm.team.repository.common.internal.queryast.Literal redactionLiteral()
      If isRedactable returns true, this method returns that literal that can be used to replace this field in a query for redaction, otherwise this method returns null.
